  "title": "SAFETY COORDINATOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Implement HSE procedures</li>\n  <li>Conduct weekly inspection with subcontractors’ supervisors</li>\n  <li>Ensure all machinery and equipment at site are in good working conditions and having all the necessary working certificates</li>\n  <li>Ensure all workers at site are wearing appropriate PPE at all times</li>\n  <li>Conduct weekly safety talk/ briefing</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper housekeeping by the subcontractors on daily basis</li>\n  <li>Conduct daily toolbox with the subcontractors</li>\n  <li>Conduct safety induction program for new workers</li>\n  <li>Conduct daily safety inspection</li>\n  <li>Advise external customers of safety needs when visiting the site</li>\n  <li>Update safety records into the safety systems</li>\n  <li>Following up on all outstanding safety related issues</li>\n  <li>Review sub-contractors’ method statements, risk assessments and safe work procedures.</li>\n  <li>Review sub-contractors’ method statements, risk assessments and safe work procedures.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Relevant Safety &amp; Health Certificates, including Building Construction Safety Supervisor Certificate and Advance Certificate in WSH or Certificate in Safety Coordinator Training Course</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of relevant experience in the construction industry</li>\n  <li>Familiar with risk management procedures</li>\n  <li>Familiar with OHSAS 18001 or ISO 14001</li>\n</ul>",
