    "description": "<p>Some 10 years ago, when the highly efficient and technically experienced team at Attika Interior + MEP was formed, an exciting journey of building a great company started. Attika Interior + MEP Pte Ltd is a full-service interior decoration and MEP engineering company with builders work experience.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3>Expertise</h3>\n<p>Our expertise and knowledge includes handling live environment projects through different phases, all aspects of fit-out and electrical works. We ensure safety on construction site and in the public areas. Our clients’ projects are in safe hands with us.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3>Accomplishment</h3>\n<p>Attika Interior + MEP Pte Ltd has completed a wide range of commercial projects for the retail and hospitality industries, schools, conversation project and office fit outs. Examples include Hotel Clover, Fort Canning Hotel and the Singapore Chinese Chamber of Commerce &amp; Industry.</p>",
